window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The journey's been Hell...but it's time to give the devil his due.</b><br> <br> This is it. This is where it all ends.<br> <br> It’s me, my shadow, and my demons against Lucifer.<br> <br> With the relics stolen, the only way to get them is to go back into the hellfire--back to Hell, where Lucifer awaits. Defeating him may mean making the ultimate sacrifice, but even with so much at stake, I don’t know if I can.<br> <br> Things heated up fast with Cain, Elias, and Dorian, and now Maverick, but I’d sell my soul a hundred times to keep them as mine. Forever.<br> <br> What if that’s impossible?<br> <br> There’s so much danger ahead of us, but I’ll bring Hell on earth to save the ones I love. I just wonder that when all’s said and done, who will be the one wearing the unholy crown?</p> <p><i>Listen to the hotter than Hell finale to the Sin Demons Series! Find out how it all ends today!</i></p> <p><b><i>Hell on Earth</i></b><b> is book six in the Sin Demons Series.</b></p>"; 
